title: Hitachi HNAS: Usage and Status of Virtual Volumes
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/storagehw/hitachi
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 Checks the Usage and Status of Virtual Volumes on Hitachi HNAS storage systems.

 It uses the check logic of the {df} check, so for configuration
 parameters and examples please refer to the man page of {df}.

 If no quota is defined or a quota without usage and limit is defined, the
 check returns the status {OK}.

item:
 The label of the virtual volume followed by the label of the physical volume
 the virtual volume belongs to.

discovery:
 One service is created for each virtual volume.
